<!doctype html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>503 - Geen toegang</title>
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://d1azc1qln24ryf.cloudfront.net/30670/Zigicons/style-cf.css?xslre9">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
            -moz-box-sizing: border-box;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        html {
            color: #000;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            background: #fff;

            line-height: 1.25;
        }
        body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .backgroundContainer,
        .contentContainer {
            width: 100%;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            display: flex;
            height: 100%;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .contentContainer-inner {
            width: 100%;
            align-self: center;
            height: 100%;
        }
        .backgroundContainer .column1 {
            background-color: #0070c0;
        }
        .backgroundContainer .column2 {
            background: #fff;
        }
        .backgroundContainer .column3 {
            background: #fff;
        }

        .columnContainer {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .column {
            width: 33.3%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .columnContent {
            align-self: center;
            padding: 0 3em;
        }
        .column2 .columnContent {
            text-align: left;
            justify-content: space-between;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: left;
            height: 50%;
        }
        .column2 .columnContent > * {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .column3 .columnContent {
            text-align: left;
            justify-content: space-between;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: left;
            height: 50%;
        }
        .column3 .columnContent > * {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .imageNoAccess {
            font-family: 'Zig';
            font-size: 330px;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .error-403 .imageNoAccess:before {
            content: "\e66a";
        }

        .error-503 .imageNoAccess:before {
            content: "\e65a";
        }

        .columnLabel {
            background-color: #0070c0;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.25em;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 20px;
        }
        .columnContent h1 {
            color: #0070c0;
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .emphasized {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .columnContent ul {
            text-align: left;
            padding-left: 2em;
        }
        .columnContent footer img {
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
        .columnText, .columnContent footer {
            line-height: 1.75em;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 900px) {
            .backgroundContainer {
                display: none;
            }
            .contentContainer {
                display: block;
            }
            h1 {
                margin-bottom: 0;
                margin-top: 1em;
            }
            p {
                margin: 1em auto;
            }
            body {
                font-size: 75%;
            }
            .contentContainer-inner {
                min-height: 100%;
                background-color: #0070c0;
            }
            .columnContainer {
                height: 50%;
            }
            .column {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 2em 0;
            }
            .column2 {
                background: #fff;
            }
            .column2 .columnContent {
                align-self: auto;
            }
            .column2 .columnContent > * {
                margin-bottom: 0px;
            }
            .column2 footer {
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
            .column3 {
                background: #fff;
            }
            .column3 .columnContent {
                align-self: auto;
            }
            .column3 .columnContent > * {
                margin-bottom: 0px;
            }
            .column3 footer {
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
        }
        @media (max-width: 550px) {
            .imageNoAccess {
                font-size: 200px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="error-503">
<div class="backgroundContainer">
    <section class="column column1"><!-- --></section>
    <section class="column column2"><!-- --></section>
    <section class="column column3"><!-- --></section>
</div>

<div class="contentContainer">
    <div class="contentContainer-inner">

        <div class="columnContainer">
            <section class="column column1">
                <div class="columnContent">
                    <div class="image imageNoAccess"></div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="column column2">
                <div class="columnContent">
                    <h2 class="columnLabel">Niet beschikbaar</h2>
                    <h1>Probeer het zodadelijk nog eens</h1>
                    <div class="columnText">
                        <p class="emphasized">We ondervinden momenteel problemen met de verbinding naar de server.</p>
                        <p>Er zit helaas niets anders op dan even te wachten.<br>
                            We doen ons best het probleem te verhelpen.<br>
                            Excuses voor het ongemak!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="column column3">
                <div class="columnContent">
                    <h2 class="columnLabel">Not available</h2>
                    <h1>Try again later</h1>
                    <div class="columnText">
                        <p class="emphasized">We are currently experiencing problems with the connection to the server.</p>
                        <p>Unfortunately, there is nothing else to do but wait.<br>
                            We do our best to solve the problem.<br>
                            Sorry for the inconvenience!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

